lay eventafter an athlete who previously swam in the river got sick, and a swimmer for Switzerland alsomissed the competitiondue to illness.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999943711672298, \"rank\": 5.2901715522254055e-06, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its team\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed relay\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"eventafter\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimmer\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitiondue\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"illness\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, Paris mayor Anne Hidalgo swam in the Seine to assure athletes about the river's safety.\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2161, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999938686388917, \"rank\": 6.131398589228751e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2173, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9942166514651409, \"rank\": 0.005816960362997569, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4